results.name: Signature-permutation of a Catalan automorphism: swap the left and right subtree of degree 2 general trees.
comment: Otherwise like automorphism *A072796, except that this involution exchanges the two leftmost subtrees of a general tree ONLY when the degree of the tree is two. Automorphism *A129608 = SPINE(*A129607) = ENIPS(*A129607). See the definitions given in A122203 and A122204.
link: A. Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2055
A. Karttunen, Prolog-program which illustrates the construction of this and similar nonrecursive Catalan automorphisms.
